2015年4月13日，曾任[[佛羅里達州眾議院|佛羅里達州眾議院]][[議長|議長]]（2006年－2008年）、現任[[美國參議員|美國參議員]]（2011年就職）以及[[美國國會及行政部門中國問題委員會|美國國會及行政部門中國問題委員會]]共同主席的'''[[馬可·魯比奧|馬可·魯比奧]]'''於[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]市中心的[[自由塔_(邁阿密)|自由塔]]宣布投入'''[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]'''<ref name="He's in">Jaffe, Alexandra; [[Dana_Bash|Bash, Dana]] (April 13, 2015) [http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/13/politics/election-2016-marco-rubio-presidential-campaign/ "He's in: Marco Rubio announces presidential bid"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/13/politics/election-2016-marco-rubio-presidential-campaign/ |date=20160304095906 }}, [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved April 14, 2015.</ref>。而在[[2012年美國總統選舉|2012年美國總統選舉]]的時候，馬可·魯比奧已經被提名為當時[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]的參選人[[米特·羅姆尼|米特·羅姆尼]]的[[美國副總統|副總統]]人選之一。因此在2016年的總統選舉中，共和黨也考慮提名馬可·魯比奧為總統候選人<ref name="Pitch">Nelson, Rebecca (April 13, 2015) [http://www.nationaljournal.com/2016-elections/marco-rubio-presidential-announcement-2016-20150413 "Marco Rubio Makes His Pitch as the Fresh Face of the GOP in 2016"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationaljournal.com/2016-elections/marco-rubio-presidential-announcement-2016-20150413 |date=20150720232732 }}, ''[[National_Journal|National Journal]]''. Retrieved April 14, 2015.</ref>。魯比奧也是第二個競選美國總統的{{link-en|古巴裔美國人|Cuban American}}。在本州[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]初選落敗後宣佈退選<ref>{{cite web|author1=Jeremy W. Peters, Michael Barbaro|title=A Distant Second at Home, Marco Rubio Ends a Disappointing Campaign|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/16/us/politics/marco-rubio.html|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316040957/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/16/us/politics/marco-rubio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
=== 2012年總統選舉 ===
[[File:Marco_Rubio_by_Gage_Skidmore_2.jpg|thumb]]
早在2011年1月，就有傳言說馬可·魯比奧可能會尋求競選總統或副總統，但之後他表示沒有興趣成爲總統或副總統候選人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Rahn|first1=Will|title=Marco Rubio: I want to be a senator, not president or vice president|url=http://dailycaller.com/2011/01/10/marco-rubio-i-want-to-be-a-senator-not-president-or-vice-president/|publisher=The Daily Caller|date=January 10, 2011|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2011-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708221150/http://dailycaller.com/2011/01/10/marco-rubio-i-want-to-be-a-senator-not-president-or-vice-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管如此，依然有許多猜測認爲[[米特·羅姆尼|米特·羅姆尼]]可能選擇他作爲競選搭檔<ref>{{cite news|last1=Roig-Fanzia|first1=Manuel|title=Marco Rubio’s compelling family story embellishes facts, documents show|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/marco-rubios-compelling-family-story-embellishes-facts-documents-show/2011/10/20/gIQAaVHD1L_story.html|publisher=The Washington Post|date=October 20, 2011|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2015-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110100424/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/marco-rubios-compelling-family-story-embellishes-facts-documents-show/2011/10/20/gIQAaVHD1L_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，魯比奧位列共和黨總統候選人[[米特·羅姆尼|米特·羅姆尼]]的副總統候選人提名名單中五人之一<ref>{{cite news |author=Sean Sullivan and Philip Rucker |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/obamas-advisers-considered-replacing-biden-with-clinton-according-to-book/2013/10/31/2f8bbf10-4285-11e3-8b74-d89d714ca4dd_story.html |title=Obama’s advisers considered replacing Biden with Clinton, according to book |publisher=The Washington Post |date=October 31, 2013 |accessdate=November 1, 2013 |archive-date=2016-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208064951/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/obamas-advisers-considered-replacing-biden-with-clinton-according-to-book/2013/10/31/2f8bbf10-4285-11e3-8b74-d89d714ca4dd_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終羅姆尼選擇了威斯康星州衆議員[[保羅·萊恩|保羅·萊恩]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Rucker|first1=Phillip|last2=Helderman|first2=Rosalind S.|title=Politics Paul Ryan is Romney’s VP pick, setting up stark choice on budget issues|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/paul-ryan-is-romneys-pick-for-vice-presidential-nominee/2012/08/11/dc2f5070-e0f1-11e1-8fc5-a7dcf1fc161d_story.html|publisher=The Washington Post|date=August 12, 2012|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001213640/http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/paul-ryan-is-romneys-pick-for-vice-presidential-nominee/2012/08/11/dc2f5070-e0f1-11e1-8fc5-a7dcf1fc161d_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2016年總統選舉 ===
[[File:Senator_of_Florida_Marco_Rubio_at_Marco_Rubio_at_the_Derry-Salem_Elks_Lodge_in_Salem_NH_by_Michael_Vadon_01.jpg|thumb]]
2015年1月，魯比奧開始準備競選總統，他接觸捐助者，並任命顧問。魯比奧還在一次籌款活動前指示他的助手「爲總統競選而準備」<ref name=Caputo>{{cite web | url=http://www.miamiherald.com/news/state/florida/article8013126.html | title=Sen. Marco Rubio to aides: ‘Prepare for a presidential campaign’ | work=[[Miami_Herald|Miami Herald]] | date=January 23, 2015 | accessdate=January 24, 2015 | author=Caputo, Marc | archive-date=2015-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212051858/http://www.miamiherald.com/news/state/florida/article8013126.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 競選活動 ==
2015年3月30日，魯比奧通過[[福斯新聞|福斯新聞]]和社交媒體表示，他將在4月13日於[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[邁阿密|邁阿密]]作出「重大公佈」。雖然他沒有說明是否涉及競選參議員連任或競選總統，大多數媒體認爲，魯比奧將宣佈參選總統。他在邁阿密市中心的自由塔宣佈了這個消息<ref name="He's in"/><ref name="Pitch"/>。魯比奧在演講中說自己具有新一代美國人的前瞻性和領導力，此外，他還宣佈不會尋求連任參議員<ref name="He's in"/><ref>{{cite news | last1=Leary | first1=Alex | title=Marco Rubio, Casting Himself as a Leader for a New Generation, is Running for President | url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/politics/stateroundup/marco-rubio-will-announce-for-president-today-in-miami/2225233 | date=April 13, 2015 | publisher=''[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]]'' | accessdate=April 14, 2015 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304082627/http://www.tampabay.com/news/politics/stateroundup/marco-rubio-will-announce-for-president-today-in-miami/2225233 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。魯比奧是第四個宣佈投入[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年總統大選]]的主要政黨成員。

